%% Diagram: Circuit breaker state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Closed

    Closed: Closed\nrequests pass through\nfailures recorded in sliding window
    Open: Open\nfast-fail every request\nno calls reach dependency
    HalfOpen: Half-Open\nlimited probe traffic\nmeasures recovery

    Closed --> Open: failure rate or slow-call rate\nexceeds threshold\n(after minimum call volume)
    Open --> HalfOpen: wait duration elapses
    HalfOpen --> Closed: probe success rate\nbelow failure threshold
    HalfOpen --> Open: any probe failure\nor slow-call ratio breach

    classDef closed fill:#2D7A2D,stroke:#1E5A1E,color:#ffffff
    classDef open fill:#B43A3A,stroke:#8E2828,color:#ffffff
    classDef halfopen fill:#8B5E15,stroke:#6E4810,color:#ffffff
    class Closed closed
    class Open open
    class HalfOpen halfopen
